<http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/CL_0000062> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "non-encoded relationships from VSAO - capable_of_producing VSAO:0000020" .
<http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/CL_0000062> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "osteoblast" .
